title: Fruit and nut pumpkin loaf cake
ingredients: ['280g plain flour', '1/2 tablespoon ground cinnamon', '1 teaspoon ground nutmeg', '1/2 teaspoon ground ginger', '1/2 teaspoon ground allspice or ground cloves', '2 teaspoons baking powder', '1/2 teaspoon salt', '2 eggs', '400g caster sugar', '425g pumpkin puree', '120ml vegetable oil', '120g dried cranberries', '120g chopped walnuts']
